1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,040
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:32,339
=Episode 1=
(At the snowy day of reunion,)

3
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:34,179
(heartbeat and tears)

4
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:36,080
(recognized you before I did.)

5
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:40,600
(Capital of Ning State)

6
00:00:42,360 --> 00:00:45,720
(Princess Chu Xihe of Ning)

7
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:05,860
(How did I end up here?)

8
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:08,820
Is anyone there? Anyone?

9
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:11,979
Open this box at once!

10
00:01:11,980 --> 00:01:13,540
Are you all deaf?

11
00:01:23,580 --> 00:01:25,500
(So you finally showed up.)

12
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:27,580
(Long time no see.)

13
00:01:27,780 --> 00:01:29,020
(My wife.)

14
00:01:29,100 --> 00:01:30,499
Did you hear me?

15
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:32,140
Let me out now!

16
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,819
(Flower Slave Tribe)

17
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:37,060
Imbeciles! How dare you abduct me?

18
00:01:59,380 --> 00:02:01,019
(I can't kill these freaks?)

19
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,380
(I can't stay here long.)

20
00:02:24,220 --> 00:02:25,660
Who sent you?

21
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,579
What do you want?

22
00:02:26,580 --> 00:02:28,139
We mean no harm.

23
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:30,300
We just need your life.

24
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,940
Who's there?

25
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:43,700
Who do you think

26
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:45,540
you are,

27
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:47,820
to dare lay a hand on her?

28
00:02:58,080 --> 00:03:01,259
(God Ye Zhao)

29
00:03:01,260 --> 00:03:02,499
- It's you?
- It's you!

30
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:04,060
Let's leave!

31
00:03:36,670 --> 00:03:41,060
ظآزWhen starlight cuts
through the long nightظآز

32
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:49,380
ظآزIt bids farewell to another blue skyظآز

33
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:52,149
ظآزTo meet is to overlapظآز

34
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,909
ظآزTo see is to part againظآز

35
00:03:53,910 --> 00:03:57,120
ظآزTo stay is to wish for foreverظآز

36
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:03,840
ظآزCounting every moment,
unwilling to pauseظآز

37
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:05,620
(Why am I crying?)

38
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:25,020
Who are you?

39
00:04:25,140 --> 00:04:27,100
I'm Ye Zhao.

40
00:04:30,300 --> 00:04:32,740
The man who swore vows with you,

41
00:04:33,780 --> 00:04:37,740
your husband bound by fate.

42
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:40,500
My wife.

43
00:04:40,940 --> 00:04:42,740
What nonsense.

44
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:45,100
Take your filthy hands off me.

45
00:04:54,580 --> 00:04:56,460
As expected of a demon,

46
00:04:57,420 --> 00:04:59,540
cold by nature.

47
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:11,740
I saved you,

48
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:15,500
yet you repay me with a blade.

49
00:05:42,180 --> 00:05:44,220
General, something's ahead!

50
00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:49,499
General, there's blood here
and bloody footprints.

51
00:05:49,500 --> 00:05:50,819
- Chase!
- Yes, sir!

52
00:05:50,820 --> 00:05:53,500
(Baobao, catch them.
Kill every Flower Slave.)

53
00:05:53,660 --> 00:05:54,820
Sure!

54
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:58,300
Stop!

55
00:06:04,780 --> 00:06:06,899
Causing trouble
in my Imperial Guard's domain?

56
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,140
Someone's got a death wish.

57
00:06:13,780 --> 00:06:14,899
Take him back.

58
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:17,219
Interrogate him
and find his accomplices.

59
00:06:17,220 --> 00:06:17,699
Yes, sir.

60
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:18,900
Take him away.

61
00:06:19,700 --> 00:06:22,219
(Divine Sword Spirit, Baobao)
Looks like I'm not needed here.

62
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,380
General.

63
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:27,280
(Commander of Imperial Guards, Pei Xiao)

64
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,899
(Imperial Guard, Li Weiguo)
What is it?

65
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:32,600
There's an order from the palace.
You're to return to the palace at once.

66
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:33,860
Back to the palace.

67
00:06:34,020 --> 00:06:35,019
Move!

68
00:06:35,020 --> 00:06:36,180
Move!

69
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,560
(Baihua Hall)

70
00:07:23,340 --> 00:07:26,180
(Chu Xihe's Consciousness)
After all these years hidden within you,

71
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:28,460
I've finally waited
for this chance to slay a god.

72
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:30,660
Let me borrow your body.

73
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:53,220
Little Immortal,

74
00:07:53,740 --> 00:07:55,620
long time no see.

75
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:23,179
My lord,

76
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:25,100
you went to such lengths

77
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:28,220
to abduct me to this desolate ruin,

78
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:31,700
only to leave me alone

79
00:08:32,700 --> 00:08:34,620
through this endless cold night?

80
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:36,260
Why not

81
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:39,140
join me in bliss?

82
00:09:10,460 --> 00:09:12,419
You're so cold.

83
00:09:12,420 --> 00:09:15,339
Am I not beautiful enough

84
00:09:15,340 --> 00:09:18,540
for you to share

85
00:09:19,140 --> 00:09:22,260
pleasure with?

86
00:09:42,500 --> 00:09:43,819
My lord,

87
00:09:43,820 --> 00:09:46,260
you're hurting me.

88
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,860
Trying to break my resolve

89
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,260
and destroy my divine heart?

90
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:53,860
A futile effort.

91
00:09:58,620 --> 00:10:00,939
Hand over your demon heart

92
00:10:00,940 --> 00:10:03,140
so I can send you to hell.

93
00:10:03,540 --> 00:10:04,740
My lord,

94
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:07,140
my heart

95
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,539
is right here.

96
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:13,300
From the moment I first saw you,

97
00:10:13,380 --> 00:10:15,260
it was

98
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:17,820
already yours.

99
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,020
If you want it,

100
00:10:21,620 --> 00:10:23,259
just take it.

101
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:24,580
You think

102
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:27,100
I wouldn't dare?

103
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:32,660
It's not that you don't dare,

104
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:35,340
but you can't bear to.

105
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,260
Even thinking of our past

106
00:10:45,020 --> 00:10:47,780
makes me sick.

107
00:10:50,580 --> 00:10:52,980
I'll rip your heart out myself.

108
00:11:01,660 --> 00:11:03,340
For a hundred years,

109
00:11:05,140 --> 00:11:06,899
day and night...

110
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:08,060
No!

111
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:09,500
No!

112
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:12,340
I've waited for this moment.

113
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:13,860
No!

114
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,229
ظآزToo bad the rain will stopظآز

115
00:11:22,230 --> 00:11:25,079
ظآزThe wind will fade,
tomorrow will clearظآز

116
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:27,819
ظآزI'd rather this night never endظآز

117
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:29,449
ظآزLet the long shadowsظآز

118
00:11:29,450 --> 00:11:35,050
ظآزwhisper what's in your heartظآز

119
00:11:35,100 --> 00:11:36,699
ظآزIf in a dreamظآز

120
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:39,459
ظآزI can hear your voiceظآز

121
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:42,309
ظآزThen let it be our meetingظآز

122
00:11:42,310 --> 00:11:44,909
ظآزLet it be usظآز

123
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:49,699
ظآزdrawing endlessly closeظآز

124
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:51,459
ظآزToo bad the rain will stopظآز

125
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:54,110
ظآزThe wind will fade,
tomorrow will clearظآز

126
00:11:54,330 --> 00:11:57,049
ظآزI can't even hold you properlyظآز

127
00:11:57,050 --> 00:11:58,699
ظآزNot even in timeظآز

128
00:11:58,700 --> 00:12:04,359
ظآزto tell you how I feelظآز

129
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,899
ظآزIf the rain won't stopظآز

130
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:08,649
ظآزIf the wind won't fade,
if time stands stillظآز

131
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:11,619
ظآزLet love go onظآز

132
00:12:11,620 --> 00:12:14,169
ظآزUntil foreverظآز

133
00:12:14,170 --> 00:12:18,809
ظآزUntil we slowly grow oldظآز

134
00:12:18,810 --> 00:12:21,419
ظآزUntil foreverظآز

135
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:28,530
ظآزUntil we slowly grow oldظآز
